{
  "stem": "8784.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One of the SS guards came running in telling the others something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at that, they released this fellow Orbach together with me, and we went back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was never tortured as this fellow Orbach was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was tortured, but he was still alive and in good shape, good enough shape that we could walk back to our barracks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we survived that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you ever find out why they took you in the first place?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rumors only.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the rumor would have it that somebody spoke of this fellow, Orbach, as a Red Orbach.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, he had red hair, and so they spoke of him as Red Orbach, meaning a communist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that supposedly was the reason for that visit and for him being tortured.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But whether this was the truth or not, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wouldn't-- I did not know it at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I still don't know whether this is the absolute truth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he was a redhead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so it took a, a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It took maybe a, a few weeks, where we remained-- this 100, this group of 100 remained inmates of Krakau-Plaszow without knowing whether Schindler is still around, whether Schindler is, is in our, in our future or not.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But lo and behold, Schindler was busy out there working to get the 100 of us out from this, from this concentration camp to come back to work for him.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after a few weeks of work and stay in Krakau, in the Krakau-Plaszow concentration camp, the 100 of us began marching out from the concentration camp to work at the enamel work factory, at the Emalia, again.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So life became, life began to look up a little bit again.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
